reviewText: Just received this 4 Audie Murphy DVD collection from Germany. Wow, the picture quality was superb not to mention the packaging. Highly recommended for Audie Murphy western lovers. You need a Multi Region DVD player.  You can get that on Amazon as well.

I remember watching most of these movies at the drive-in theater when I was young and they're just as much fun for me now as they were then.  If you're an Audie Murphy fan and you have a region free DVD player they're well worth the money.  The packaging was an extra treat with each disc placed in a foldout of the original movie poster.  I was very pleased with the entire package.
Great collection - arrived on the first day of the window
